Ezeckiel or Ezechiel__34.2__Shepherds: : That is, princes, magistrates, chief priests, and scribes.
Ezeckiel or Ezechiel__34.23__David: : Christ, who is of the house of David.
Ezeckiel or Ezechiel__34.29__A bud of renown: : Germen nominatum. He speaks of Christ our Lord, the illustrious bud of the house of David, renowned over all the earth. See Jer. 33. 15.
